---
description: Asks the model to structure its response as markdown with specific named sections.
vars:
  - name: sections
    type: list
    description: Ordered list of section headings the response must contain.
    min: 1
---
## Output format

Structure your response as markdown with the following sections, in order.
Each section must contain at least one paragraph.

{% for s in sections %}- ## {{ s }}
{% endfor %}
